data.description: This 3/1.5/4 Car Garage and Sunroom sits in Nederlands Songwood Addition. Laminate wood in living room opens to sunroom for additional living space. Kitchen is precious with oak cabinets, granite countertops, and newer Kenmore stainless steel appliances.Oven is gas with 5 burner and convection. French door refrigerator with bottom freezer stays with home. Extra side drive brings you through a covered area to the 2nd full 2 car garage. Backyard has commercial grade dog kennels. So much for the price.
